HEADWORD: Rinforzando
<hw>Rin`for*zan"do</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[It., fr.
<ets>rinforzare</ets> to reenforce, strengthen.]</ety> <fld>(Mus.)</fld>
<def>Increasing; strengthening; -- a direction indicating a sudden
increase of force (abbreviated <abbr>rf.</abbr>, <abbr>rfz.</abbr>) Cf.
<er>Forzando</er>, and <er>Sforzando</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

